title: Playmakers - S01E09
description:
Season 1 - Episode 9 of 11

This hard-hitting drama follows a group of professional football players as they deal with the downside of hitting the big time. The star running back has a drug problem, one of the defensive players has a problem with anger, and one player is gay, but trying to hide is sexuality. Because of their celebrity and the demands of the job, all the players are on a journey to balance professional and personal success.
